Name: dev scripts
Installation: brew install openssl libyaml libffi readline zlib xz; xcode-select --install;

Name: node
Installation: brew install gpg gawk; asdf plugin add nodejs https://github.com/asdf-vm/asdf-nodejs.git; asdf install nodejs latest

Name: python
Installation: asdf plugin-add python; asdf install python 3.13.3; asdf global python latest;

Name: ruby
Installation:
asdf plugin add ruby https://github.com/asdf-vm/asdf-ruby.git
asdf install ruby 3.1.3
asdf global ruby 3.1.3
asdf shell ruby 3.1.3

Name: rust
Installation: asdf plugin add rust https://github.com/code-lever/asdf-rust.git; asdf install rust latest; asdf global rust latest;

Name: go
Installation: asdf plugin add golang https://github.com/kennyp/asdf-golang.git; asdf install golang latest; asdf global golang latest
